window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>She was always the one who got away.</p> <p>Rosaleigh caught my eyes from the beginning, but I didn't make my move. She was too young. Unfortunately, my best friend didn't have the same morals. It killed me, watching from a distance as he disrespected the woman who was always meant to be mine.</p> <p>When she finally discovers the truth about him, all bets are off. I'm done holding back. I make my move, ready to prove she has a real man now—one who will have her back and give her the life she deserves.</p> <p>I won't let anything stop me. She's not getting away again. I'm going to make her mine.</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
